Package com.example.appointment.controller

Interface AppointmentDataInterface

All Superinterfaces:
SQLControllerInterface
All Known Implementing Classes:
AddAppointmentController, ModifyAppointmentController
public interface AppointmentDataInterface extends SQLControllerInterface
An interface that is used to load data for the Add Appointment, and Modify Appointment controllers. This interface exists to compartmentalize some of the more technical code from the controller, so the controller can be more tailored to a specific need.
